SELECT MIN(t.title) AS typical_european_movie
FROM company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     title AS t
WHERE ct.kind = 'production companies'
  AND mc.note LIKE '%(theatrical)%'
  AND mc.note LIKE '%(France)%'
  AND mi.info IN ('Sweden',
                  'Norway',
                  'Germany',
                  'Denmark',
                  'Swedish',
                  'Denish',
                  'Norwegian',
                  'German')
  AND t.production_year > 2005
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id;

SELECT MIN(t.title) AS typical_european_movie
    FROM company_type AS ct,
        info_type AS it,
        movie_companies AS mc,
        movie_info AS mi,
        title AS t
    WHERE ct.kind = 'production companies'
    AND mc.note IS NULL
    AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Thriller')
    AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1980 AND 1984
    AND t.id = mi.movie_id
    AND t.id = mc.movie_id
    AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
    AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
    AND it.id = mi.info_type_id;

    FROM company_type AS ct,
        info_type AS it,
        movie_companies AS mc,

    WHERE ct.kind = 'production companies'

    AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Denish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American')
    AND t.title != '' AND (t.title LIKE 'Champion%' OR t.title LIKE 'Loser%')
    AND t.id = mi.movie_id
    AND t.id = mc.movie_id
    AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
    AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
    AND it.id = mi.info_type_id;
